SELECT
  CASE
    WHEN ABS(tip - real_tip) / real_tip * 100 < 10 THEN '< 10%'
    WHEN ABS(tip - real_tip) / real_tip * 100 < 20 THEN '10% - 20%'
    WHEN ABS(tip - real_tip) / real_tip * 100 < 30 THEN '20% - 30%'
    WHEN ABS(tip - real_tip) / real_tip * 100 < 40 THEN '30% - 40%'
    WHEN ABS(tip - real_tip) / real_tip * 100 < 50 THEN '40% - 50%'
    ELSE '> 50%'
  END AS percent_error_bucket,
  COUNT(*) AS count
FROM
  predictions
WHERE predicted_at AT TIME ZONE 'Europe/Paris' >= $__timeFrom()
GROUP BY
  percent_error_bucket
ORDER BY
  percent_error_bucket;

SELECT
  'RMSE' AS data,
  SQRT(AVG(POWER(tip - real_tip, 2))) AS rmse
FROM
  predictions
WHERE predicted_at AT TIME ZONE 'Europe/Paris' >= $__timeFrom()

WITH training_stats AS (
    SELECT
        'training' AS data,
        AVG(tip) AS mean_tip,
        PERCENTILE_CONT(0.5) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY tip) AS median_tip,
        STDDEV(tip) AS tip_std,
        3*(AVG(tip) - PERCENTILE_CONT(0.5) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY tip))/STDDEV(tip) AS skewness
    FROM training_data 
),
prediction_stats AS (
    SELECT
        'predictions' AS data,
        AVG(tip) AS mean_tip,
        PERCENTILE_CONT(0.5) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY tip) AS median_tip,
        STDDEV(tip) AS tip_std,
        3*(AVG(tip) - PERCENTILE_CONT(0.5) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY tip))/STDDEV(tip) AS skewness
    FROM predictions
    WHERE predicted_at AT TIME ZONE 'Europe/Paris' >= $__timeFrom()
)
SELECT * FROM training_stats
UNION ALL
SELECT * FROM prediction_stats

SELECT

WITH training AS (
  SELECT 100*SUM(CASE WHEN sex = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(*) AS female_percent,
         100 - 100*SUM(CASE WHEN sex = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(*) AS male_percent
  FROM training_data
),
pred AS (
  SELECT 100*SUM(CASE WHEN sex = 'Female' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(*) AS female_percent,
         100 - 100*SUM(CASE WHEN sex = 'Female' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)/COUNT(*) AS male_percent
  FROM predictions
  WHERE predicted_at AT TIME ZONE 'Europe/Paris' >= $__timeFrom() 
)
SELECT 'training' AS data, female_percent, male_percent
FROM training
UNION ALL
SELECT 'predictions' AS data, female_percent, male_percent
FROM pred

WITH training AS (
  SELECT 
    1.0 * SUM(CASE WHEN sex = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / NULLIF(COUNT(*), 0) AS expected_female,
    1.0 * SUM(CASE WHEN sex = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / NULLIF(COUNT(*), 0) AS expected_male
  FROM training_data
),
pred AS (
  SELECT 
    1.0 * SUM(CASE WHEN sex = 'Female' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / NULLIF(COUNT(*), 0) AS actual_female,
    1.0 * SUM(CASE WHEN sex = 'Male' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / NULLIF(COUNT(*), 0) AS actual_male
  FROM predictions
  WHERE predicted_at AT TIME ZONE 'Europe/Paris' >= $__timeFrom()
),
psi_calc AS (
  SELECT
    -- Avoid division by zero and log of zero with CASE WHEN
    CASE 
      WHEN expected_female > 0 AND actual_female > 0 
      THEN (actual_female - expected_female) * LN(actual_female / expected_female)
      ELSE 0 
    END AS psi_female,
    
    CASE 
      WHEN expected_male > 0 AND actual_male > 0 
      THEN (actual_male - expected_male) * LN(actual_male / expected_male)
      ELSE 0 
    END AS psi_male
  FROM training, pred
)
SELECT 
  'psi' AS data,
  psi_female + psi_male AS total_psi
FROM psi_calc;
